📍 El Rey Mexican Bar & Grill 
904 Seventh St
Novato, Ca 

This place was delicious and the drive was so beautiful it’s worth the trip! We heard the drinks are fire and their Sunday buffets are delicious and there is so much selection! My bestie and I took the drive to see what the hype was all about and it was totally worth it! This place is perfect for a date night or dinner with the family! They have a full bar and the service was amazing! I love supporting family owned businesses and I encourage everyone to go check them out! I promise you will love the food ! Order the El Rey Margarita and the fully loaded guacamole 🥑 it’s soooo tasty! They definitely have great Sazon over there !
